1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the use of cloud computing in HetNets to improve network performance, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture.
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses techniques to improve spectral and energy efficiencies, which are related to information theory.
3. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking) - The paper discusses the use of cloud computing in communication networks, which falls under the scope of communications and networking.
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses the use of cloud computing in distributed networks, which falls under the scope of distributed computing.
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses techniques to improve network performance, which can be related to systems and control.
